Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:10.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:49.82,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)}We Won't Lose to You
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.73,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What? Captain Vangeance from the Golden Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:12.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's also the leader of the \NEye of the Midnight Sun, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.48,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,"William is asleep inside \Nme," is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So his body was taken over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:26.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he's not the \Nonly one who went all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It affected other Magic Knights, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:32.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Marx, Old Man Owen,\Nand the Spiny Prickly Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Even Captain Charlotte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:45.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of crap happened while you \Nwere enjoying your beauty sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:47.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You do realize I was dying, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:51.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,At least sound like you mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:01.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you weren't taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Does that mean Langris's \Nbody was also taken over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:06.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:13.93,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That ominous mana... Is that \Nwhy he tried to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:18.89,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.93,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.93,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:37.23,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Explosive Scattershot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:53.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, you virgin delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I was heading back from visiting Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.74,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be all \Nalone and crying somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:08.76,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is crying?! And get \Nthe hell off my Crazy Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Just don't get \Nin the way of my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:21.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Right about now, Asta, \NNoelle, and Luck are fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.38,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,the guys from the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:24.91,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:31.06,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make sure I don't embarrass\N them as their senior knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.63,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.06,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll make it back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So head on back first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuno! Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:07.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. None of us know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.58,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you it was futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.38,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time we made you quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus, please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.26,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:49.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Klaus! We're both Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:55.58,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This body is... reacting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:06:00.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Our hatred for you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.29,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,is far stronger than your \Npathetic little bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:24.02,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. If you push yourself \Ntoo hard, you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.11,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:33.49,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we won't need you anymore \Nonce we get your grimoire and swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.96,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like you're going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.46,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.37,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to protect your precious \Nlittle royal friend and die,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.30,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.01,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.60,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:08.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I promised my friends I'd come back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let my friends kill my other friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:15.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll survive this. I'll survive all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:27.33,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.13,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're poor, an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.85,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,or even us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:37.62,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can become greater than anyone \Nelse in this world. And to prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:41.46,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To make Sister and everyone else happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.73,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:58.29,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you babbling about \Nnow, when you can hardly even move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.91,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,This is where...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.66,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,...you're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.17,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going \Nto become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.53,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuno?! Y-You... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you... Are you actually Yuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.92,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:49.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But your ears are hella pointy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, apparently they are. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But, I mean... you're normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.58,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.26,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Yuno! Our ears match!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Bell, could you quiet down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for that, Miss Spirit Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:06.73,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.83,main,Bella,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:13.16,main,Bella,0000,0000,0000,,Stop staring at the little shrimp \Nand look at how much I've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:16.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you calling a shrimp?!\NYou're {\i1}way{\i0} smaller than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.64,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're both way too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.51,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:25.66,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Would one of you kindly \Nget me down from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm me. You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.76,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck are you two having a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.50,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, look at m—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.50,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So you've awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:45.64,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of us. Now, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.44,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.11,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not butt in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:57.00,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,This mana... The reincarnation \Ndefinitely worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.19,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like he's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:06.01,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht's grimoire and swords are right \Nin front of him, and he hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.34,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it could be because he used the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:13.24,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,ultimate forbidden spell to \Nbring back his elf friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:16.34,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they might need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:20.06,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Both Licht... and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.23,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:27.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What's moving their bodies right now \Nare souls that belong to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:31.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus and Hamon's souls have been put to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:35.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Then we can save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.57,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.49,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,And also inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:42.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.51,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Magic Knight of \Nthe Clover Kingdom, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.00,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:57.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, that vessel is a human \Nwith a very strong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:00.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he hasn't fully awakened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are such a nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:09.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to kill those two behind you,\N and then have you leave that body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.98,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:20.52,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Those bodies belong to my senior knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.46,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to give it everything we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The ground's shaking just from \Nyou guys glaring at each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.41,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how we're going \Nto get them out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We may have to incapacitate and bind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You take Mimosa and get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.36,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm gonna let you do this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.62,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's not alone! He has me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, this might be rough, \Nbut step back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.28,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,With the grimoires and \Nknowledge from this age,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we will be able to use even more \Nrefined spells than existed in our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.95,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:31.49,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combination Spell: Le Chateau de Verre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that thing sure looks crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You got this, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.53,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's some intense magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have time to cover you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.03,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Le Chateau du Verre!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.55,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.55,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You two are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.30,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The anti-magic kid is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.81,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,but that other guy who hasn't \Nfully awakened even though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.89,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,his magic grew exponentially after \Nbeing reincarnated is a pain, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.42,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:15.95,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even using magic, and he's \Nable to make himself and others float?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.96,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.\NHis mana is so incredibly dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:34.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And that sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! What?! What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Stop that, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.37,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.87,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's incredible magic \Ncoming from that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:03.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap... My black form\N is reaching its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.38,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Just last a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This goes way beyond fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:19.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he melted into the air. \NI can't even read his ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:23.38,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though he became one with \Nthe mana of nature itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.01,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense his mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:25.08,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Spirit Binding Magic: Liable Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound like you, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.93,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:05.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.96,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do about \Nthat guy's teleporting, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna surpass my limits right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Spirit Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.94,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He sucked up my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:10.40,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,This is just one of the \NDemon-Dweller Sword's true powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.19,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:38.10,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And what the heck's going on with my sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.93,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on in general?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:45.54,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Don't stop moving \Nat a time like this, body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:50.76,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,That brat's probably reached \Nhis limits... though, so have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.31,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him credit for \Ngetting this far, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.78,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.53,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wanted to try \Nhealing them, my magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.12,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find an opening with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.35,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.81,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.57,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.18,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.32,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,He's starting to keep up with \Nhow fast those attacks are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.07,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.45,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.83,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.83,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mana Zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.89,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's that one lady's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.13,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.72,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:14.26,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing enough that he \Nmanaged to find an opening
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:17.38,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,with Licht, even though he hasn't \Ncompletely awakened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.23,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect nothing less from Licht's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.69,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.74,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he couldn't move anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:36.50,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is when Asta will surpass his limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.76,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Their timing is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.51,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.29,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:07.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He blocked our attack with that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.73,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's condensing a phenomenal \Namount of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.05,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:43.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun, Licht, is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:46.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I promised Zora I would come back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:48.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I've got Yuno, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:52.32,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 101: \N"The Lives of the Village in the Sticks."
